metadata.name: LIZZIE BENNETT #1
metadata.description:
The Lizzie Bennett collection is 333 unique photo art cards of women created by Irina Chuzh, hand-made using different style traits. They live in the metaverse of the ETH blockchain.

We were inspired by Elizabeth Bennett's character from Pride and Prejudice, which is a shining example of self-control, feminine dignity, readiness, devotion to family, and loyalty to herself. The qualities inherent in the main character were not brought up in her by her family or invested by her teacher, which proves once again: everything is in our hands. Her self-education, the ability to hold herself favorably distinguished her from the rest of her family and surroundings.

We have tried to convey in our collection all that Elizabeth Bennett impressed us with her personality. This character is a good example of how you can forgive, compromise, and respect yourself. We hope you will find your Elizabeth.
